Who in the hell would steal a school district media library's version of Hamlet?&nbsp;

It was there when I did my inventory in July, no one has requested it and no one else has even inquired about it.&nbsp;

Why is it not on my shelf! Why can't I trust schoolteachers?

Grr, I am going to request that my collection be locked up at night. Who knows what else is missing.
